      "content": "In Toronto, the escrow agent is usually a licensed and regulated third-party service provider, often a mortgage broker or a real estate company with an escrow department. These agents are required to be transparent and accountable, and they typically have a separate account specifically for escrow funds. They are also required to follow strict guidelines and regulations to ensure the funds are handled safely and securely. This way, the money is protected and not vulnerable to loss or mismanagement.",
